{"tid":734514,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英格蘭瑞典戰球場多空位 因德國球迷大量退飛","createTime":"2018-07-08T16:26:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T07:21:46.000Z","uid":55981,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"526a5ef5179d4874478c6cdb6601c317503152ca","tid":734514,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T16:26:36.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=oym2T%2F0Q7q2FF4yFJ3Qu6%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=c6c35eec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】英格蘭在周六世界盃8強硬撼瑞典，這樣重要的比賽，現場卻出現甚多空位，何解呢？<br />\n<br />\n原來因為德國早早出局！根據《太陽報》報道，因為大量德國球迷非常有信心，認為球隊可以以F組首名出戰，一路殺入這場8強戰，所以早早就購買了比賽門票。 誰知德國只能夠在F組包尾出局，而瑞典就以首名出線，再於16強以1:0擊敗瑞士，取代德國晉身這場8強戰。眼見愛隊未能出戰，因此有大約1萬張門票，早前被德國球迷退回予國際足協。同時間，英格蘭球迷卻只能從足總買得2500張波飛。由於有大量退票，因此在開賽前，仍然有不少門票可供購買 在這場沒有德國的比賽，英格蘭憑中堅哈利馬古尼、中場迪利阿里在上下半場各建一功，以2:0輕取瑞典，繼1990年後再次殺入4強。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/NINTCHDBPICT000418771577-e1530972871695.jpg?w=960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesun.co.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2FNINTCHDBPICT000418771577-e1530972871695.jpg%3Fw%3D960&h=5328296b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/NINTCHDBPICT000418771549-e1530972952321.jpg?w=960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesun.co.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2FNINTCHDBPICT000418771549-e1530972952321.jpg%3Fw%3D960&h=14995de4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/NINTCHDBPICT0004187744461-e1530973748684.jpg?w=960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesun.co.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2FNINTCHDBPICT0004187744461-e1530973748684.jpg%3Fw%3D960&h=56053fc8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"abc9b0916fe7ab68582d1e6b68656065b91215ba","tid":734514,"uid":38793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited